des:
New music radio station in Raleigh, NC. Playlist with the likes of Jason Isbell, Nathaniel Rateliff, Avett Brothers, The Decemberists and Ryan Adams.

Once you've enabled the skill, you can say "Alexa, open that station“ to start listening.
